metadata.name: Child time
metadata.description:
We are born against our will and get into a world full of garbage, far-fetched ideas and rules invented by someone, bad ecology, and yet life is beautiful.

Interesting fact, in two months, when I have just begun to draw a sketch of this work, we found out that my wife is pregnant. My son will be one year old on February 15.

Mp4 / 3000x3000
